The Nord Theme extension for LibreOffice introduces an elegant, north-bluish clean aesthetic to your office suite, featuring both the highly optimized Nord Dark and Nord Light color schemes. Designed strictly according to the official Nord palette guidelines, this extension delivers maximum visual comfort, enhanced workspace hierarchy, and meticulous contrast adjustment to eliminate eye strain during prolonged typing sessions. It seamlessly unifies your document view, interface components, and application backgrounds, while providing full semantic syntax highlighting for the BASIC macro editor to ensure a highly focused, modern, and distraction-free environment for authors, analysts, and developers alike.